@startuml
actor Pengguna
participant View
participant Controller
participant Model
participant Database

Pengguna -> View : Akses halaman Pesanan\nPilih pesanan selesai/dibayar\nKlik "Cetak/Unduh Invoice"
View -> Controller : GET /orders/{id}/invoice

Controller -> Model : get_invoice_data(id)
Model -> Database : query (Item, Harga, Ongkir, Pembeli, Penjual)
Database --> Model : result
Model --> Controller : result

Controller -> Controller : Generate dokumen Invoice (HTML/PDF)
Controller --> View : Return file/preview Invoice
View --> Pengguna : Tampilkan preview atau mulai unduh

Pengguna -> View : Simpan atau cetak file Invoice
@enduml
